waterfox (6.5.1-0) obs; urgency=medium

    * You should now see a Table of Contents in the Preferences page, for easier navigation of settings.
    * You can now set any URL as the new tab page by setting the browser.newtab.url preference in about:config.
    * The old school password manager has been re-implemented, available at about:passwords.
    * The old school configuration manager has been re-implemented, available at about:cfg. Thanks to @black7375 for the help with this.
    * Updated the JPEG-XL library to the latest version. This should stop various websites that serve .jxl files from crashing in the tab they’re loaded.
    * The missing strings for Look & Feel page are now no longer missing, meaning you can change your theme preferences once again.

